5.1 AUTOMATIC TERMINATION

Any breach of this License results in IMMEDIATE AND AUTOMATIC
termination of all rights granted herein — without notice, without
a cure period, and without any action required by the Licensor.

Upon termination, you must immediately cease all use of the Software
and destroy all copies in your possession or control.

5.2 DAMAGES

Violations constitute copyright infringement and may also constitute
misappropriation of trade secrets, breach of contract, and unfair
business practices under applicable law.

In the event of a violation, the Licensor is entitled to seek:

(a) Immediate injunctive relief to stop unauthorized use;

(b) Actual damages, including all profits derived from
unauthorized use;

(c) Statutory damages under the U.S. Copyright Act (17 U.S.C. § 504)
of up to $150,000 per work infringed for willful infringement;

(d) Attorney's fees and all costs of litigation;

(e) Any other relief a court of competent jurisdiction deems just.

5.3 WILLFULNESS PRESUMPTION

Any party that accesses this repository in any way — including
viewing, cloning, forking, or downloading — is conclusively presumed
to have read and understood this License in full.

Unauthorized use beyond passive viewing is therefore presumed WILLFUL,
entitling the Licensor to seek maximum statutory damages of $150,000
per infringed work without requiring proof of actual notice.

